{"search_data": "Central [Apply] Baal Aadhaar Card Online Application Form 2020 | UIDAI Blue Coloured Card for ChildrenUIDAI invites Baal Aadhaar Card online application form 2020 at nearby located aadhaar seva kendras, apply for blue coloured aadhaar card for new born babies and children below 5 years of age, check supporting documents list \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Baal Aadhaar Card Apply Online Form 2020Below is the complete process to fill online application form for Baal Aadhaar Card:-Firstly visit the official website at uidai.gov.inAt the homepage, click at the \u201cGet Aadhaar\u201d link and in the new window, click at the \u201cBook An Appointment\u201d link.Direct Link \u2013 https://appointments.uidai.gov.in/bookappointment.aspxHere people can \u201cBook an Appointment at UIDAI run Aadhaar Seva Kendra\u201d by entering their city / location. In addition to this, people can even Book an Appointment at Registrar run Aadhaar Seva Kendra.Then click at \u201cProceed to book Appointment\u201d tab to open the Baal Aadhaar Card online application form for booking appointment.UIDAI Baal Aadhar Card Apply Online FormHere candidates can enter the mobile number and verify OTP to open the appointment booking page as shown below:-Baal Aadhar Card Appointment Booking FormHere fill in all the details to book an appointment for Aadhaar Seva Kendra. Then take your child to the Aadhaar Seva Kendra at that particular time slot.UIDAI has provided this facility of booking an appointment at an Aadhaar Seva Kendra for various Aadhaar services. These includes fresh aadhaar enrolment, update of name, address, mobile number, e-mail ID, date of birth, gender and biometric (Photo + Fingerprints + Iris).Baal Aadhar Card Documents ListPeople can make Aadhaar Card of their new born babies just with the help of Discharge Slip of Hospitals. If the discharge slip is not present, then apply for Baal Aadhaar Card through Birth Certificate in addition to aadhar card of one of the parents. Moreover, children school identity card could also be used to apply for Baal Aadhar Card.Baal Aadhar Card Documents List\u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u093e \u0906\u0927\u093e\u0930 \u0909\u0928\u0915\u0947 \u091c\u0928\u094d\u092e \u092a\u094d\u0930\u092e\u093e\u0923 \u092a\u0924\u094d\u0930 (\u0905\u092d\u093f\u092d\u093e\u0935\u0915 \u0915\u0947 \u0906\u0927\u093e\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u0925) \u092f\u093e \u092b\u093f\u0930 \u0905\u0938\u094d\u092a\u0924\u093e\u0932 \u0938\u0947 \u0921\u093f\u0938\u094d\u091a\u093e\u0930\u094d\u091c \u0915\u093f\u090f \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0947 \u0926\u094c\u0930\u093e\u0928 \u092e\u093f\u0932\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0940 \u092a\u0930\u094d\u091a\u0940 (\u0921\u093f\u0938\u094d\u091a\u093e\u0930\u094d\u091c \u0938\u094d\u0932\u093f\u092a) \u0915\u0940 \u092e\u0926\u0926 \u0938\u0947 \u092c\u0928 \u091c\u093e\u0924\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 For more details, call on the UIDAI Aadhaar Toll Free Number at 1947.#AadhaarForMyChildA child below 5 years gets a blue coloured #BaalAadhaar, which is valid till the child becomes 5 yr old. A mandatory biometric update is required to reactivate the child's Aadhaar. For this, take the child to any nearby Aadhaar Kendra: https://t.co/QFcNEqehlP pic.twitter.com/nGcIc2bvYe\u2014 Aadhaar (@UIDAI) February 11, 2020 The blue coloured baal aadhaar card needs to be updated when children becomes 5 years of age. This card is to be once again updated on attaining the age of 15 years.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://www.jansatta.com/utility-news/how-to-enroll-for-aadhaar-of-new-born-babies-at-uidai-and-aadhaar-seva-kendra/1314300/  at  "}